            <h1>
                The Benefits to HR for Using eKnowID</h1>
            <h3>
                Pain</h3>
            <div>
                Current model of pre-screening candidate who have already been screened several
                all using various tools and mechanism does not make any sense as it causes delays,
                aggravation, loss productivity and opens up to possible lawsuits (see pepsi.).
            </div>
            <h3>
                By the stats</h3>
            <div>
                <ul class="ulDiscType">
                    <li class="font_weight_normal">Since birth a person will potentially have nearly 100
                        types of background checks conducted on them in their lifetime for various purposes
                        (eg school, medical, housing, tenant, licensing, jobs memberships).</li>
                    <li class="font_weight_normal">Errors abound from every where, Human error, improper
                        database inquiries (see boston bomber), criminal identity theft (nearly 12 million
                        new people reported being affected last year alone).</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <h3>
                Solution</h3>
            <div>
                One independently vetted portal that will allow you to accurately verify your applicant’s
                information per FCRA requirements and avoid all the, time delay, cost, regulation
                burdens.
            </div>
            <h3>
                Benefits</h3>
            <div>
                <ul class="ulNumberType">
                    <li>Time - <span class="font_weight_normal">Receive report Instantly from prescreened
                        candidate as oppose to typical wait of up to 72 sometime 2 weeks(for intl) to receive
                        reports. </span></li>
                    <li>Increase Productivity - <span class="font_weight_normal">Gain ability to expedite
                        onboarding to get new employee started up 3-5 days earlier than to wait for them
                        to clear screening process. </span></li>
                    <li>Money<br />
                        <ul class="ulNumberType">
                            <li class="list_style_circle">Lower cost to retrieve reports on pre-screened candidates
                                Pay less per report.</li>
                            <li class="list_style_circle">Lower administrative cost on process background checks
                                by allowing applicant to pre-complete data entry process. </li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>Reduced Legal Liability -<span class="font_weight_normal"> Reduce exposure to wrongly
                        denying a person a job either due to inaccuracy or rely on incorrect information.
                    </span></li>
                    <li>Better Accuracy - <span class="font_weight_normal">Assured better accuracy by having
                        the dispute vetting process pre-handled by applicant. </span></li>
                    <li>Improved Compliance -<span class="font_weight_normal"> Know that the compliance
                        has been applied uniformly based on federal, state and local laws regarding your
                        candidate. </span></li>
                    <li>Reliability -<span class="font_weight_normal"> Independently vetted by a private
                        detective agency. </span></li>
                    <li>Integration Capabilities - <span class="font_weight_normal">We integrate with most
                        major ATS platforms including taleo and People to provide streamline process. </span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
